Jenkins Notification Listener 

Listens on notification from Jenkins Notification plugin on port 3002

Build image:
./build.sh

Debug app (on developer laptop):
JENKINS_API_KEY=<API-KEY> USER=<CDSID> ./debug.sh

Run app in production (gotsvl1416):
- Login to server gotsvl1416.got.volvocars.net
- sudo su - jenkins-icup_android
- cd /cm/services
- repo sync --no-clone-bundle vendor/volvocars
- cd jenkins_notification_listener
- ./build.sh
- JENKINS_API_KEY=<Jenkins API KEY> USER=<CDSID> ./run.sh
- tail -100f log/jenkins_notification_listener.log

Restart example (build & run):
docker kill $(docker ps --filter ancestor=jenkins-notification-listener --format "{{.ID}}") && ./build.sh && USER=E9426001 ./run.sh

